<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē vasunāgabhūśaśimitē śrīmānasākhyānvayā śrīmaṁggīśvaravallabhā guṇavatī lakṣmīti nāmōjvalā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīsiṁhyādripatērnṛsiṁhyavapuṣō dīpadvayārtthaṁ ddadau
<lb n="2"/>grāmammaṇḍapanāmadhēyamamalaṁ gō paṁcchavi<unclear>ṁ</unclear>śadvayaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śakavarṣaṁbulu 1188 gunēṇṭi mēṣasaṁkrāntimodalugā rāpaṟti maṁggirājula mahādēvulu lakṣmīdēvulu tama koḍku Upēṁdra
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rājulaku nāyurārōggyaiśva<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>yyābhivṛddhigā śrīsiṁhyagirināthuni nagariyaṁddu reṁḍu Akhaṁḍadīpamulakuṁgāṁ beṭṭina mōdālu Eṁbhayini 50 Okka dīpadaṁḍunu nīdēva
<lb n="4" break="no"/>raku naivēdyārtthamugā nāhaṟupākanāṁḍuṁ gaṭṭulōni maṇapamaneḍi Ūru Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigāṁ beṭṭe Ī dharmmuvu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śatruṇāpi kritō dharmma Anu nyāyamu paripāliṁccunadi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

